These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, tea, cola
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, pakistani, chinese, indian
1. the person drinking tea is between the chinese and the pakistani##2
2. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the chinese##3
3. the chinese is not to the left of the chinese##8
4. the pakistani is not the person drinking tea##6
5. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
6. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | cola  | fanta | tea | iced-tea  |
| Nationality   | italian | chinese   | indian  | pakistani |

