.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
House: farmhouse, palace, cottage, cape-cod
City: paris, boston, venice, marseilles
1. the person traveling to marseilles is not to the left of the person traveling to marseilles##8
2. the farmhouse house is somewhere to the right of the cape-cod house##5
3. the farmhouse house is the person traveling to boston##1
4. the cape-cod house is between the farmhouse house and the palace house##2
5. the palace house is somewhere between the cottage house and the person traveling to paris##7
6. the person traveling to venice is somewhere to the left of the palace house##5
7. the person traveling to paris is not to the left of the person traveling to paris##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| House   | cottage | palace          | cape-cod | farmhouse     |
| City    | venice      | marseilles | paris | boston |

