.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, singing, writing, filmmaking
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, zinnia, aconite, orchid
1. the person who growsbellflower is not to the left of the person who's hobby is writing##8
2. the person who growszinnia is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is in an even position##4
5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere to the left of the person who growsorchid##5
7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person who growsaconite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Hobby           | reading | singing | writing     | filmmaking |
| Flower   | zinnia    | orchid   | bellflower | aconite    |

