.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
4 different games are played: bridge, chess, snooker, scrabble
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, fonseca, alhambra, old-henry
1. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
2. the davidoff-smoker is not to the left of the fonseca-smoker##8
3. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the person playing chess##1
4. the person playing scrabble is not to the right of the alhambra-smoker##8
5. the person playing bridge is the davidoff-smoker##1
6. the person playing bridge is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
7. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the left of the person playing scrabble##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Game   | snooker   | chess         | scrabble   | bridge    |
| Cigar         | fonseca | old-henry | alhambra | davidoff |

