.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, board-games, cooking, skydiving
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, jet-ski, train, van
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is board-games##7
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the left of the person driving the train##5
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person who's hobby is video-games##7
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is not to the left of the person driving the van##8
5. the person driving the van is somewhere between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person driving the jet-ski##7
6. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
7. the person driving the jet-ski is not to the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##8
8. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | board-games   | cooking | skydiving | video-games    |
| Transport         | boat | van   | train   | jet-ski |

