.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-6::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, bluemaster, alhambra, cain
4 different games are played: domino, chess, billiard, backgammon
1. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
2. the person playing chess is somewhere to the left of the chaman-smoker##5
3. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
4. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
5. the chaman-smoker is somewhere to the left of the bluemaster-smoker##5
6. the cain-smoker is not to the left of the person playing chess##8
7. the cain-smoker is the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Cigar          | cain | chaman | bluemaster  | alhambra |
| Game   | chess   | backgammon         | billiard | domino |

