.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, strawberry, tomato, eggplant
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, fuchsia, light-blue, white
1. the person who likes fuchsia is not to the left of the person eating strawberry##8
2. the person who likes white is somewhere between the person eating eggplant and the person who likes light-blue##7
3. the person who likes light-blue is somewhere to the right of the person who likes red##5
4. the person who likes white is not to the left of the person who likes red##8
5. the person who likes white is not to the left of the person eating strawberry##8
6. the person eating lime is on the left or right of the person eating tomato##3
7. the person who likes red is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
8. the person eating lime is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Food   | strawberry      | tomato | lime | eggplant   |
| Color      | red | light-blue | white  | fuchsia |

