3. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
4. the person watching satire movies is somewhere between the person watching crime movies and the person drinking mirinda##7
5. the person drinking cola is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
6. the person drinking water is somewhere between the person watching crime movies and the person drinking cola##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |      2       |        3        |     4      |
