.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, biathlon, skateboarding, basketball
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, mango, pumpkin, kale
1. the person who's sport is sailing is between the person who's sport is basketball and the person eating raspberry##2
2. the person eating kale is on the far left##1
3. the person eating kale is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
4. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the right of the person eating raspberry##5
5. the person eating mango is the person eating mango##1
6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not the person eating pumpkin##6
7. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##8
8. the person eating raspberry is not to the left of the person eating mango##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Sport   | basketball   | sailing | skateboarding | biathlon |
| Food     | kale | mango       | raspberry  | pumpkin    |

