.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-12::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, techno, r&b, trance
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, bird, frog, turtle
1. the fan of r&b is not to the right of the owner of the turtle##8
2. the owner of the hedgehog is not to the right of the fan of techno##8
3. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the right of the fan of trance##5
4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left or far right##3
5. the fan of r&b is between the owner of the turtle and the owner of the frog##2
6. the fan of techno is on the far left##1
7. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre    | techno        | trance | r&b      | electronic    |
| Pet   | hedgehog | frog   | bird | turtle |

