.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, reggae, rock, punk
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, skateboard, helicopter, quad-bike
 1. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the helicopter##5
 2. the fan of punk is not to the left of the fan of rock##8
 3. the fan of disco is the person driving the helicopter##1
 4. the person driving the helicopter is not to the right of the person driving the skateboard##8
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
 6. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the right of the fan of rock##5
 7. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the fan of disco is not to the right of the person driving the helicopter##8
 9. the person driving the skateboard is not to the left of the fan of disco##8
10. the fan of reggae is not to the left of the person driving the bus##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Music-Genre          | reggae    | rock | disco | punk |
| Transport   | bus | quad-bike  | helicopter     | skateboard    |

