.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-17::.
There 4 different types of food: kale, cauliflower, cucumber, pineapple
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, july, october, june
1. the person who's birthday is in july is not to the left of the person eating cauliflower##8
2. the person who's birthday is in july is not to the left of the person eating cauliflower##8
3. the person who's birthday is in october is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##8
4. the person eating cucumber is not the person who's birthday is in june##6
5. the person eating pineapple is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in june##8
6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far right##1
7. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
8. the person eating cucumber is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |    4    |
| Food           | cucumber | pineapple | cauliflower | kale   |
| Birthday   | october       | june      | july    | august |

