2. the person who's sport is volleyball is not to the left of the person who likes green##8
3. the person who likes green is the person who likes green##1
4. the person who likes white is the person who's sport is baseball##1
5. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
6. the person who's sport is sailing is between the person who likes green and the person who's sport is baseball##2
7. the person who's sport is volleyball is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Sport    | baseball        | sailing | skateboarding | volleyball |
| Color   | white | emerald | green   | brown    |

