2. the fan of ambient is not to the right of the person playing backgammon##8
3. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere between the person playing backgammon and the person playing billiard##7
4. the fan of funk is somewhere to the right of the person playing domino##5
5. the fan of funk is somewhere to the left of the fan of folk##5
6. the fan of disco is not to the right of the fan of funk##8
7. the person playing mah-jongg is not to the left of the fan of folk##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Game         | domino  | billiard | mah-jongg  | backgammon  |
| Music-Genre   | disco | funk   | folk | ambient |

