.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, ambient, electronic, r&b
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, dahlia, bellflower, orchid
1. the person who growsdahlia is not the fan of trance##6
2. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
3. the fan of r&b is not to the left of the person who growsorchid##8
4. the fan of electronic is the person who growsazalea##1
5. the fan of r&b is somewhere between the person who growsdahlia and the person who growsazalea##7
6. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of trance##1
7. the person who growsbellflower is between the person who growsorchid and the fan of electronic##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre         | ambient    | r&b | trance | electronic |
| Flower   | dahlia | orchid      | bellflower     | azalea     |

 